    \n                \n                \n                \n                </li>\n            </ul>\n        </li>   \n        <li class=\"title\">\n\n            <a class=\"a\" href=\"../../tzgg.htm\" title=\"通知公告\"><h3>通知公告</h3></a><i></i>\n        </li>   \n    </ul>\n</nav>\n<section class=\"nav_mask\"></section>\n\n<!--============================头部 结束=============================-->\n\n\n<!--============================主体 开始=============================-->\n\n<section id=\"banner\" class=\"banner\">\n     <ul class=\"slow_miso miso-initialized miso-slider\">\n        <div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"miso-list draggable\"><div class=\"miso-track\" role=\"listbox\" style=\"opacity: 1; width: 1280px; transform: translate3d(0px, 0px, 0px);\"><li class=\"miso-slide miso-current miso-active\" data-miso-index=\"0\" aria-hidden=\"false\" tabindex=\"-1\" role=\"option\" aria-describedby=\"miso-slide00\" style=\"width: 1280px;\">\n <a tabindex=\"0\">\n            <img src=\"../../images/banner/ban7ner.jpg\" alt=\"\"> </a>\n        </li></div></div>\n    </ul> \n\n</section>\n<script>\n$(\".banner ul\").miso({\n    dots:true\n});\n</script>\n\n<section class=\"miso_content\">\n\n<section class=\"n_container n_lvli_detail\">\n    <div class=\"w1200\">\n        <div class=\"content\">\n            <div class=\"bg\"></div>\n            <div class=\"content_li\">\n                <div class=\"title001\">\n                    <h3>\n\n\n\n研究系列</h3>\n                </div>\n \n             \n                <div class=\"fl00 fl01 clearfix\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/engine.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js\"></script><link href=\"/system/resource/style/component/news/content/format4.css\" type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><form name=\"_newscontent_fromname\">\n<div class=\"left fl\">\n                        <div class=\"img slow fl\">\n                                                    <img src=\"/__local/5/94/08/A6FD2930C1C162EB8402CEC443B_9A3D9385_44FAC.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-bottom: #39b54a 3px solid;\">\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"con fr\">\n                            <h3>王小虎</h3>\n                            <dl><dd>清华大学基础医学院，副研究员</dd>\n                            \n                            </dl>                            \n                            <p>\n                                <b>Contact Us：</b><br>\n                                Tel: +86-10-62798973<br>\n                                E-mail:  wangxhu@tsinghua.edu.cn<br>\n                                Address：中国北京市海淀区清华大学医学科学楼D312\n                            </p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"right fr\">\n \n       \n\n       \n\n\n\n\n<div id=\"vsb_content_4\"><div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<div>\n <h4 style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">教育背景</h4>\n <p>1994-1998 武汉大学遗传学专业 学士</p>\n <p>1998-2001 中科院水生生物研究所 硕士</p>\n <p>2001-2007 美国贝勒医学院 博士</p>\n <h4 style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">工作经历</h4>\n <p>2007-2009 美国贝勒医学院 博士后</p>\n <p>2009-2014 美国德州大学安德森癌症研究中心 博士后</p>\n <p>2014-2024 清华大学医学院 副研究员</p>\n <p>2024-至今 清华大学基础医学院 副研究员</p>\n <h4 style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">研究领域</h4>\n <p>主要从事T细胞与炎症疾病领域的研究。长期关注Th17细胞分化发育过程中的转录、表观、代谢和分子调控机制等方面的研究，以理解其在人类相关疾病中的功能及调控机制。未来拟重点开发基于Gibbs自由能(ΔG)的高通量实验方法，并通过结合生信技术，精准确定转录因子或DNA结合蛋白的功能靶点，构建基因调控网络，了解其在重要生理活动和人类疾病中的功能。</p>\n <h4 style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">科学贡献</h4>\n <p>系统解析了Th17细胞的首要转录因子RORγt和特征细胞因子IL-17相关的顺式和反式调控机制，发现多个顺式DNA调控元件，并揭示了其在Th17分化发育过程中的转录、表观和分子调控机制。曾首次揭示发烧与自身免疫疾病之间存在因果关系（Immunity, 2020)，相关发现曾被F1000Prime、Nature Reviews Immunology、Immunity、Science Immunology、ImmunoBites等10余家国内外学术杂志和媒体予以评论和推荐，并被评选为“细胞杂志出版社2020中国年度论文”。到目前为止，共计发表SCI论文40余篇，包括多篇Nature、Immunity等杂志论文,总引用2000余次。</p>\n <h4 style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">荣誉奖励</h4>\n <p>2012年，美国多发性硬化症协会，博士后基金</p>\n <p>2021年，“细胞杂志出版社2020中国年度论文”</p>\n <h4 style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">代表性论文</h4>\n <p>1.Chang D, Zhang H, Ge J, Xing Q, Guo X, Wang X*, Dong C*. A cis-element at the Rorc locus regulates the development of type 3 innate lymphoid cells. Front Immunol. 14,1105145 eCollection (2023).</p>\n <p>2.Chi X, Jin W, Zhao X, Xie T, Shao J, Bai X, Jiang Y, Wang X*, Dong C*. RORγt expression in mature TH17 cells safeguards their lineage specification by inhibiting conversion to TH2 cells. Sci Adv. 8(34), eabn7774 (2022).</p>\n <p>3.Chang D, Xing Q, Su Y, Zhao X, Xu W, Wang X*, Dong C*. The Conserved Non-coding Sequences CNS6 and CNS9 Control Cytokine-Induced Rorc Transcription during T Helper 17 Cell Differentiation. Immunity 53, 614-626 (2020).</p>\n <p>4.Wang X<sup> </sup># *, Ni L#, Wan S, Zhao X, Ding X, Dejean A, Dong C*. Febrile temperature critically controls the differentiation and pathogenicity of T helper 17 cells. Immunity 52, 328-341(2020)</p>\n <p>5.Xu T#, Stewart KM#, Wang X#, Liu K, Xie M, Kyu JK, Li K, Ma T, Wang H, Ni L, Zhu S, Cao N, Zhu D, Zhang Y, Akassoglou K, Dong C, Driggers EM, Ding S. Metabolic control of TH17 and induced Treg cell balance by an epigenetic mechanism. Nature 548, 228-233 (2017)</p>\n <p>6.Wang X*, Ni L, Chang D, Lu H, Jiang Y, Kim BS, Wang A, Liu X, Zhong B, Yang X, Dong C*. Cyclic AMP-Responsive Element-Binding Protein (CREB) is Critical in Autoimmunity by Promoting Th17 but Inhibiting Treg Cell Differentiation. EBioMedicine 25:165-174 (2017).</p>\n <p>7.Wang X and Dong C. The CD70-CD27 axis, a new brake in the T helper 17 cell response. Immunity 38, 1-3 (2013).</p>\n <p>8.Wang X, Zhang Y, Yang XO, Nurieva RI, Chang SH, Ojeda SS, Kang HS, Schluns KS, Gui J, Jetten AM and Dong C. Transcription of Il17 and Il17f is controlled by conserved noncoding sequence 2. Immunity 36, 23-31 (2012).</p>\n <p>9.Xu T#, Wang X#, Zhong B, Nurieva RI, Ding S, Dong C. Ursolic acid suppresses interleukin-17 (IL-17) production by selectively antagonizing the function of RORgamma t protein. J Biol Chem. 286, 22707-10 (2010).</p>\n <p>10.Wang X, Gao H, Shen Y, Weinstock G, Zhou J, and Palzkill T. A high-throughput percentage-of-binding strategy to measure binding energies in DNA-protein interactions: application to genome scale site discovery. Nucleic Acids Res. 36, 4863-71 (2008).</p>\n <p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">11.Gao H#, Wang X#, Yang Z. K, Palzkill T and Zhou J. Probing regulon of ArcA in Shewanella oneidensis MR-1 by integrated genomic analyses. BMC Genomics 9, 42 (2008)</p>\n</div>\n</div></div><div id=\"div_vote_id\"></div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n      \n\n</form>\n\n                      \n                    </div>\n                                      \n                </div>\n          <section class=\"n_sanji\">\n<ul style=\"    height: 44px;\">\n    <li><a href=\"../../szdw/jcyxy.htm\" title=\"教职员工\">教职员工</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"../../szdw/jzjs.htm\" title=\"兼职教授\">兼职教授</a></li>\n</ul>\n                  \n                </section>\n\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"mianbao\">\n            <div>\n     您现在的位置： \n                        <a href=\"../../index.htm\">首页</a>\n               <i>&gt;</i>\n                <a href=\"../../szdw/jcyxy.htm\">师资队伍</a>\n               <i>&gt;</i>\n                <a href=\"../../szdw/jcyxy.htm\">基础医学院</a>\n               <i>&gt;</i>\n                <a href=\"../../szdw/jcyxy/yjxl.htm\">研究系列</a>\n               <i>&gt;</i>\n                正文\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"content_li1\"></div>\n        </div>\n    \n</section>\n<script>\n$('.miso_hd ul').miso({\n    autoplay:false,\n    slidesToShow: 3,\n    waitForAnimate: false,\n    asNavFor:$('.miso_bd')\n});\n$('.miso_bd').miso({\n    autoplay:false,\n    waitForAnimate: false,\n    adaptiveHeight:true,\n    asNavFor:$('.miso_hd ul')\n});\n</script>\n\n\n</sectio